EN: On the other hand, her voice is more pleasant to listen to.

ZH: 这个城市的交通状况非常拥堵，相比之下，乡村的道路宽敞畅通。
EN: The traffic in this city is very congested; in contrast, the roads in the countryside are spacious and clear.

ZH: 相比之下，这辆新车价格实在太高了。
EN: Comparatively, the price of this new car is just too high.

ZH: 这篇文章的内容生动有趣，相比之下，那篇就显得有些乏味了。
EN: The content of this article is lively and interesting; by comparison, the other article seems a bit dull.

ZH: 这款手机的外观设计很漂亮，相比之下，功能就显得有些简单了。
EN: The appearance design of this mobile phone is very beautiful; in contrast, the functions seem a bit simple.

